Plot.
When the evil spirit Pitch Black, known by the children of the Earth as the 
Boogieman, begins an attack, the Guardians - Santa Clause (North), The Tooth 
fairy, The Easter Bunny, and the Sandman - must invite another, new Guardian 
for help. When they attempt to add Jack Frost, he refuses out of spite that he 
isn't good enough. As the Guardians fight Pitch Black and convince Jack that 
he is good, the children slowly stop believing in them. Jack must help the 
Guardians restore their magic with the children of Earth so they can continue 
protecting the children from danger. When the evil spirit Pitch launches an 
assault on Earth, the Immortal Guardians team up to protect the innocence of 
children all around the world.
